narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: YES. Any class with Anna Betbeze
Definitely! Interesting and not a lot of work!

Color is fantastic if you can get in. It's very competitive, but not too bad for seniors and art majors. It's a really enjoyable class to take for a little something different. The projects aren't easy, but they also don't take a ton of time.
